Name: Assassin's Creed III: The Tyranny of King Washington: The Redemption
Overview: The Tyranny of King Washington - Part 3: The Redemption is a downloadable content (DLC) for Assassin's Creed III. Ratonhnhaké:ton’s journey concludes in the third and final episode. Arriving in New York, Ratonhnhaké:ton will call upon all of the abilities tied to his native heritage in order to break into the monarch fortress and put an end to the tyranny of King Washington.
